name: Ichinose Asuna | 一之瀬アスナ (Blue Archive)
description:
First character LoRA, the one and only maid with the brightest grin.

(02/06/2023) - Apparently civitai had secretly deleted the samples for maid + bunny suit. Guys for real do you hate big boobas or lolis just pick one.

Samples tested at 1 strength on Anything v4.5, AOM3A1B, and Counterfeit 2.5.

Use these trigger words to get Asuna's characteristics:

  • 1girl, asuna, blue eyes, long hair, halo, hair over one eye

Extra prompts you can use for her:

  • very long hair, light brown hair, large breasts, mole, mole on breast, hair ribbon

Some outfits that she can use:

Maid Outfit:

  • maid, maid headdress, apron, frills, frilled apron, puffy sleeves, short sleeves, white gloves, white thighhighs

Bunny Outfit:

  • rabbit ears, blue leotard, playboy bunny, black pantyhose, white gloves

School Uniform:

  • school uniform, white shirt, sleeves rolled up, black choker, black skirt, blue bowtie

Have fun!
